== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正}} 6th year（[[Julian calendar]] [[1578]] [[December 4]]） – [[Oda Nobunaga]]’s naval forces engage the [[Mōri clan]] in battle and defeat the [[Mōri navy]].
== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保}} 2nd year（[[Gregorian calendar]] [[1717]] [[December 8]]） – [[Nagakubo Sekisui]] (長久保赤水), geographer and Confucian scholar (d. [[1801]]).
== Deaths == * [[Kenpō (era)|Kenpō]] 2nd year（[[Julian calendar]] [[1214]] [[December 8]]） – [[Sasaki Takatsuna]] (佐々木高綱), samurai of the late Heian and early Kamakura period (b. [[1160]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}} 1st year（[[Gregorian calendar]] [[1848]] [[December 1]]） – [[Kyokutei Bakin]] (滝沢馬琴), novelist and author of *Nansō Satomi Hakkenden* (b. [[1767]]).
